content: I'm planning a summer trip to Europe with my family and I'm looking for some help with finding the best flights. I've been doing a lot of domestic travel lately, by the way - in addition to the Chicago flights, I've taken four more domestic flights to other cities, including two to New York, one to Los Angeles, and one to Dallas. Do you have any recommendations for good flight search engines or travel websites that can help me find deals on international flights?
